<a href="https://pubads.g.doubleclick.net/gampad/jump?iu=0&sz=1&c=234" target="_blank"><img src="https://pubads.g.doubleclick.net/gampad/ad?iu=0&sz=1&c=234" border="0" alt=""></a>Union Information Agency quoted media reports saying the founder of the MMM series of financial pyramid schemes, Sergei Mavrodi, died in Moscow on Monday. Moskovsky Komsomolets also reports that Mavrodi was taken to a city hospital after he felt weakness and pain in the chest area.The emergency team has failed to save his life. "He died this morning," the report said. Wikipedia also says Mavrodi was born on 11 August 1955 and died on 26 March 2018.In 2007 Sergei Mavrodi was convicted in a Russian court of defrauding 10,000 investors out of 110 million rubles ($4.3 million).Mavrodi was born in Moscow. According Wikipedia Mavrodi was diagnosed with a bilateral heart defect during his childhood.In school he was proficient in mathematics and physics and studied at the Moscow State Institute of Electronics and Mathematics.In 1983 he was arrested for 10 days due to illegal economic activity.